name: Lifeproof Iphone 5 Skin(only) Ohana Collection by Courtney Martin
description:
Ohana Creations by artist Courtney Martin

I pratice in multi-medium: murals in homes, charcoal drawings, watercolor and acrylic pantings, stone carving, pottery, saltwater fish mosaics, custom mosaic kitchens and bathrooms, free hand artist, I keep it funky fresh :).
Biography
Every being has a purpose and was put here to make a difference.

I'm a Firefighter/Paramedic fulltime and a surfer, fisherman, and an artist at heart. I started creating art at a very young age, I was always too outdoorsy to actually take up in any formal training, this I believe makes me and my art unique. I've come to a crossroads in my life where I'm living my life for me and taking advantage of my independence and opportunities presented while they last. I love meeting new people. I live for tomorrow because I'm so excited to see what the future holds, I still dream of one day having my own happy ending. I'm tattooed with a full sleeve in progress down my right arm inspired by my artwork. I've over come two injuries that almost cost me my life and my entire career, I grow stonger by the day. My entire family is full of surfer's and fishermen, I was raised by two very respected parents who taught me to always love myself. Independence and hard work will gain you respect.

Phone (863) 899-1302
Email Ohanacreations@aol.com
Website http://www.OhanaCreationsFL.com

name: Lifeproof Bar mount
description: Throw away that plastic bag! With the LifeProof Bike and Bar Mount for your iPhone 4/4S Case, you will be able to bring your mobile device on that biking adventure in any weather conditions. Designed for both pedal bikes and Motorbikes, the LifeProof Bike & Bar Mount allows you to place your device on your handlebars in landscape or portrait orientation. You can map out your routes on GPS, measure the distances you have traveled, and even listen to your favorite tunes on speaker! The LifeProof Bike & Bar Mount allows you to conveniently place and remove your device with one hand through a quick release locking mechanism, giving you the ability to fully focus on enjoying the ride. Works great on shopping carts too!
